{"tid":836414,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人有恐血症(heterophobia)?","createTime":"2018-09-25T15:21:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T00:38:36.000Z","uid":113250,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1081a35951a551bb06f9affcf3317a3c20de5cb3","tid":836414,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T15:21:31.000Z","msg":"先利申, 未正式diagnosed, 所以更加想搵下連登有無同類既人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n恐血症有唔同的類型, 有人怕自己既血, 有人怕人地既血。講返自己, 每次整親(覺得好痛) + 見到自己既血(不論多少), 就會喺幾分鐘內面青頭暈, 有時會暈到行唔到同埋嘔。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過只要見唔到自己既血, 例如撞親, 或者流血但唔覺得太痛, 咁就無事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一句講哂, 真係好撚麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece20706d0a942168d6312bed09164dcb8f96d3f","tid":836414,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T15:22:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"932185d5e5558e1c43a55cdee37c7438f22bc935","tid":836414,"uid":82710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T15:23:23.000Z","msg":"紅色有咩好驚"},{"pid":"7e513cb9c56b9d6edced64817ec638ffe3b4cc0f","tid":836414,"uid":113250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"932185d5e5558e1c43a55cdee37c7438f22bc935","tid":836414,"uid":82710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T15:23:23.000Z","msg":"紅色有咩好驚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T15:25:05.000Z","msg":"補充句, 其實係無驚既感覺, 但就係控制唔到頭暈。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52501cb0c1de6a449dd7ae35cd221bc410385a0f","tid":836414,"uid":3037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T15:26:12.000Z","msg":"見到血/傷口會好唔舒服好想嘔好想逃離現場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f270a7238ea3a73a4e26e4609b06e3bbe7ec3a33","tid